And if you'd like, you can add a fade track to fade up from black.

43
00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:28.920
The structure of a nested level sequence can be nearly anything, especially for game construction

44
00:03:28.920 --> 00:03:35.240
purposes, but for cinematics and linear content creation there are usually some core ingredients.

45
00:03:35.240 --> 00:03:39.520
Inside each level sequence shot, you'll have level actors like props or characters to

46
00:03:39.520 --> 00:03:40.520
