With a single camera cuts track and a single level sequence, users can construct long animated

55
00:04:19.660 --> 00:04:24.199
takes and assign cuts to the camera cuts track to meet their needs.

56
00:04:24.199 --> 00:04:28.639
If multiple cameras are added into the level sequence, that long animated take can easily

57
00:04:28.639 --> 00:04:32.879
turn into a master shot with coverage cameras being placed throughout the scene and bound

58
00:04:32.879 --> 00:04:38.399
to the camera cuts track to create an engaging sequence where continuity is easily preserved.

